    "There is a scarcity of open-source instruction datasets related to programming languages, primarily tailored for specific application scenarios.",
    "(6) The number of general-domain datasets is 67, aligning with the widespread demand for instruction fine-tuning techniques in various application scenarios.",
    "Research and construction of instruction datasets for relevant LLMs have also been conducted in common fields such as healthcare, programming, law, etc.",
